==English==
===Etymology===
Latin "wasting away"

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /'teɪbi:z/

===Noun===
'''tabes'''
#''(medical)'' A kind of slow [[bodily]] [[waste#Verb|wasting]] or [[emaciate|emaciating]] disease, often accompanying a [[chronic]] disease.

